# coder tokens create

Create a tokens
## Usage
```console
coder tokens create [flags]
```

## Local Flags
| Name |  Default | Usage |
| ---- |  ------- | ----- |
| --lifetime | 720h0m0s | <code>Specify a duration for the lifetime of the token.<br/>Consumes $CODER_TOKEN_LIFETIME</code>|
